==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''croquet'''
# A [[game]], played on a [[lawn]], in which players use [[mallet]]s to drive [[wooden]] [[ball]]s through [[hoop]]s ([[wicket]]s)
# A [[shot]] in this game in which the [[opponent]]'s ball is driven away by hitting one's own ball when they are in contact
# A [[croquette]]

===Transitive verb===
'''to croquet'''
# to drive away an opponent's ball in the above manner

